OL,3,CThe physical, psychological and social
OL,4,Cwounds suffered by children in Lebanon
OL,6,FIsrael's ongoing attacks in southern
OL,7,FLebanon and on the capital Beirut have
OL,8,Fraised fears that the country could be
OL,9,Fturned into another Gaza.
OL,11,FWarning: this report from our
OL,12,FInternational Editor Emma Murphy
OL,13,Fstarts with footage of the children's
OL,14,Fcovered bodies being carried for their
OL,15,Ffunerals
OL,17,FSometimes it's the asides which are
OL,18,Fthe most disturbing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
