OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773753074
OL,3,CThe physical, psychological and social
OL,4,Cwounds suffered by children in Lebanon
OL,6,FToday we interviewed Dr Ghassan Abu
OL,7,FSitta, a combat surgeon who has spent
OL,8,Fmuch of the last few years treating
OL,9,Fchildren in Gaza and is now in Lebanon
OL,10,Ftreating the children of this war.
OL,12,FWe were looking at a scan of an 11-
OL,13,Fyear-old girl's face.
OL,15,FThe white marks on the image were
OL,16,Fshrapnel in her cheeks, a larger white
OL,17,Fmark detailed the shrapnel that had
OL,18,Ftorn into her eye socket and destroyed
OL,19,Fthe eye completely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773753074
OL,3,CThe physical, psychological and social
OL,4,Cwounds suffered by children in Lebanon
OL,6,FAnd then we looked at the image of her
OL,7,Fmouth.
OL,9,F"I need to go and operate on her after
OL,10,Fthis," Dr Abu Sitta told me. "Her
OL,11,Fmouth is like a bag of broken bones."
OL,13,FI don't know if it was his words or
OL,14,Fthe look on his face which knocked me
OL,15,Fso sick. What a journey this little
OL,16,Fgirl has ahead.
OL,18,FAll the operations, all the pain, all
OL,19,Fthe trauma and at the end a face that
OL,20,Fwill carry the scars of this war long
OL,21,Fafter it has ended.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@FO]rD@^OUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
