CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773753074
OL,3,CThe physical, psychological and social
OL,4,Cwounds suffered by children in Lebanon
OL,6,FHe fitted in our interview between
OL,7,Ftreating a family with three siblings
OL,8,Fand a mother needing surgery. The
OL,9,Ffourth child has died. This is just
OL,10,Fone family of many now needing
OL,11,Fspecialist care.
OL,13,FDr Abu Sitta has seen what war does to
OL,14,Fyoung bodies and is seeing it again,
OL,15,Fbut this time in Beirut at least,
OL,16,Fthere is a difference from the war of
OL,17,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773753074
OL,3,CThe physical, psychological and social
OL,4,Cwounds suffered by children in Lebanon
OL,6,F"In the previous war there weren't as
OL,7,Fmany shrapnel injuries. My feeling is
OL,8,Fthat the previous war, because it
OL,9,Finvolved a lot of ground penetrating
OL,10,Fbunker busters, the kind of explosive
OL,11,Fand the effect of the shrapnel flying
OL,12,Feverywhere was less," he told me.
OL,14,F"Now, the percentage of children is
OL,15,Fmuch higher. Israel killed 100
OL,16,Fchildren in Lebanon in the last two
OL,17,Fweeks. And so the types of injuries
OL,18,Fare closer to that we saw in Gaza than
OL,19,Fin the previous Lebanese wars."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@UO]vD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
